    • Method Detail

      • fieldOfMessage

        public static FieldAccess fieldOfMessage(MessageAccess message,
                                         io.spine.code.proto.FieldDeclaration field)
        Creates a new FieldAccess.

        If the given field is singular, the expression yields the value of the field.

        If the given field is repeated, the expression yields the list of values of the field.

        If the given field is a map, the expression yields the collection of values of the field, without the keys.

        Parameters:
        message - an expression of the message to obtain the field from
        field - the field
        Returns:
        new FieldAccess
